    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >问候，罗多维亚的继承人。你准备好宣称你的合法王位吗？如果是的话，请知晓——统治一个幻想王国可不是一件容易的事。欢迎来到《贪婪之冠》，一款受老派传统启发的经典策略游戏，具有独特的间接指挥系统，这在其他策略游戏中十分少见。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/7f5409bf2f1ffb978b5b0febf88823d6.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/c341a8ce3202b90dee1361d91cb32e90.poster.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/c341a8ce3202b90dee1361d91cb32e90.webm?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/c341a8ce3202b90dee1361d91cb32e90.mp4?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >试试作为统治者的手腕</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划、建设和扩展你的幻想王国，用各种可升级的建筑填充它。从广泛的经济设施、工作坊、军事建筑和英雄住宅中选择，以确保人民的安全和福祉。他们的感激将以丰厚的税收形式回报你，只有你可以使用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/70f9a0997559e032f6c60adc35ee42ae.webp?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=2 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/708b3755f7896e0678524a40307949fa.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/d3d81fa68f1d755dcdee90a855a5e132.poster.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/d3d81fa68f1d755dcdee90a855a5e132.webm?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/d3d81fa68f1d755dcdee90a855a5e132.mp4?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >他们会同意为你服务吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄们拥有自由意志，会乐意接受你的任务……或者不会！你不能强迫他们服从，但可以尝试用闪亮的金币购买他们的服务。记住，每个英雄类别都专门针对不同类型的任务——无论是侦查、摧毁敌人的栖息地、保卫城市还是与特定敌人作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/70f9a0997559e032f6c60adc35ee42ae.webp?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=2 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/589846d6e8662bbc5b7ef3487e1a5b23.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/0b73362669f11e575c3222ba67ecb13d.poster.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/0b73362669f11e575c3222ba67ecb13d.webm?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/0b73362669f11e575c3222ba67ecb13d.mp4?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >受欧洲中世纪民间文化启发的领域在等待你</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越阴暗、神秘的罗多维亚土地，增强你的统治。探索多种生物群落，如密林、死亡之地、沼泽、冰原或平原，每个地区都有其独特的位置和可怕的居民。参观被遗忘的废墟、洞穴、墓地或巢穴，并记住——冒险与回报并存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/70f9a0997559e032f6c60adc35ee42ae.webp?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=2 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/60731e1f836a3273c43ed28fefadaaaa.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/54c29993e03dc85c401b88bcea3a36be.poster.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/54c29993e03dc85c401b88bcea3a36be.webm?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/54c29993e03dc85c401b88bcea3a36be.mp4?t=1760114467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不再发出直接命令</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现权威不仅仅是命令，国王的权力只有在他能够使他人屈服于自己的意志时才会强大。你的臣民和独立英雄将自己决定他们想先执行哪些任务——良好的规划因此是你成功的关键之一！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/70f9a0997559e032f6c60adc35ee42ae.webp?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=2 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307570/extras/21ba47e97f179727bd60b9b9314cef1b.avif?t=1760114467\" width=600 height=75 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不寻常的实时策略游戏玩法，提供间接管理解决方案</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吸引人的命令系统，可能影响或不影响你的臣民和英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建设和扩展自己的幻想据点的机会</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态的战斗和魔法系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雄伟的游戏世界，灵感来自欧洲中世纪民间文化和神话</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可升级的城市中心，玩家可以在任务之间访问</p></li></ul>",
